OL,3,CMillions of customers facing parcel
OL,4,Cdelivery problems - here's how to
OL,5,Csolve them
OL,7,FBy Olivia Mustafa, ITV News Producer
OL,9,FWith Christmas around the corner and
OL,10,FBlack Friday approaching, parcel
OL,11,Fdelivery firms are facing their
OL,12,Fbusiest time of year - but 15 million
OL,13,Fcustomers had delivery problems in the
OL,14,Fpast month, Citizens Advice has found.
OL,16,FThe organisation's annual parcels
OL,17,Fleague table ranked Yodel and Evri at
OL,18,Fthe bottom, with two stars out of five
OL,19,Feach, while Amazon and Royal Mail came
OL,20,Ffirst, with three stars.
