OL,7,FHowever, all of those firms saw their
OL,8,Fcustomer service scores drop from last
OL,9,Fyear, with only DPD's score remaining
OL,10,Fthe same.
OL,12,FCustomers have faced problems such as
OL,13,Fparcels being left out in the open and
OL,14,Farriving late - and the number of
OL,15,Fpeople experiencing further issues
OL,16,Fwhen trying to solve the issue is at
OL,17,Fits highest level in three years.
