OL,3,CMillions of customers facing parcel
OL,4,Cdelivery problems - here's how to
OL,5,Csolve them
OL,7,FFigures from Ofcom last month found
OL,8,Ftwo thirds of people have had problems
OL,9,Fwith delivery in the previous six
OL,10,Fmonths, and the regulator said it has
OL,11,Fstrengthened regulations on parcel
OL,12,Fcompanies to ensure consumers are
OL,13,Ftreated fairly.
OL,15,FHere are some tips on how to dodge
OL,16,Fparcel delivery issues.
OL,18,FApproach the seller
