OL,3,CMillions of customers facing parcel
OL,4,Cdelivery problems - here's how to
OL,5,Csolve them
OL,7,FCheck delivery information
OL,9,FMake sure you're clear on how much
OL,10,Fdelivery will cost and how long it
OL,11,Fwill take before ordering an item. It
OL,12,Fis also worth researching the
OL,13,Fcompany's return and refund policies.
OL,15,FDeliver it elsewhere
OL,17,FJane Parsons, a consumer expert from
OL,18,FCitizens Advice, suggests looking into
OL,19,Ffinding an alternative delivery
OL,20,Faddress if you're likely to be out of
OL,21,Fthe house when it arrives.
