OL,4,Cdelivery problems - here's how to
OL,5,Csolve them
OL,7,FShe said: "Consider asking a neighbour
OL,8,For friend if it can be delivered to
OL,9,Ftheir address.
OL,11,F"But beware, if you do provide details
OL,12,Fof a safe space or nominated neighbour
OL,13,Fand something goes wrong with those
OL,14,Farrangements, it's not the seller or
OL,15,Fcourier's responsibility."
