OL,5,Csolve them
OL,7,FOnline traders or private seller?
OL,9,FYour consumer rights remain the same
OL,10,Fwhether you're buying online or in-
OL,11,Fperson from a shop.
OL,13,FCheck whether you're buying from a
OL,14,Fprivate seller or a trader. Try to
OL,15,Ffind if the platform has a process to
OL,16,Fresolve disputes which might make
OL,17,Fthings easier if there's a problem
OL,18,Fwith a private seller.
OL,20,FConsider reviews
